http://www.atr.org:80/townhall/FRC/insight/is95b2wl.html 204.71.237.87 19970210001518 text/html 21391
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 00:16:03 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Mar-96 16:16:05 GMT
