&quot;report of Board of Inquiry ICO LCDR Kenneth A. Carkhuff,&quot;
June 16, 1995: 170, 173.
<P>
<LI>Ibid. p 157.
<P>
<LI>Ibid. p 158.
<P>
<LI>Ibid. p 180.
</OL>
</font>

<p>

